---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="FAQ - Money Mastery Resources">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Financial Education -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-4 text-xl font-semibold">Financial Education</h2>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">What financial topics do you cover?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">We cover a wide range of topics including credit repair, wealth building, budgeting, debt management, investing basics, and financial mindset development.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">Are your resources suitable for beginners?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Yes! Our content is designed to be accessible for beginners while also providing valuable insights for those with more financial experience.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Credit Repair -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-4 text-xl font-semibold">Credit Repair</h2>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">How can I improve my credit score?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Our Credit Repair Magic program provides a comprehensive system for improving your credit score through legal methods, dispute strategies, and positive credit building techniques.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">How long does credit repair take?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">While results vary by individual, many users see improvements within 3-6 months of following our credit repair strategies consistently.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Wealth Building -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-4 text-xl font-semibold">Wealth Building</h2>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">What is the Wealth Switch program?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">The Wealth Switch is our revolutionary program that helps you transform your money mindset and develop wealthy habits through proven psychological techniques and practical strategies.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">Can anyone build wealth?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Yes! We believe wealth building is accessible to everyone with the right mindset, knowledge, and tools. Our programs are designed to help you regardless of your starting point.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Support -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="bg-primary-600 text-white px-6 py-4 text-xl font-semibold">Support & Resources</h2>
          <div class="p-6 space-y-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">How can I get help with your programs?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Each of our programs includes comprehensive support through detailed guides, video tutorials, and our responsive customer service team.</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg text-gray-900">Do you offer refunds?</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">Yes, we stand behind our products with a satisfaction guarantee. Please refer to each product's specific terms for detailed refund policies.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-8">Ready to Transform Your Financial Future?</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="md:flex h-full">
              <div class="md:w-1/2 relative overflow-hidden">
                <img 
                  class="h-64 md:h-full w-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105" 
                  src="/images/credit-repair.jpg" 
                  alt="Credit Repair Magic product image"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent md:hidden"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="md:w-1/2 p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Credit Repair Magic</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Transform your credit score with our proven, AI-powered credit repair system. Boost your financial potential today!</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <a 
                    href="http://credit.crimsonedgeventures.com" 
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-primary-600 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-700 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200"
                  >
                    Get Started Now
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="md:flex h-full">
              <div class="md:w-1/2 relative overflow-hidden">
                <img 
                  class="h-64 md:h-full w-full object-cover transform transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105" 
                  src="/images/wealth-mindset.jpg" 
                  alt="Wealth Switch product image"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/30 to-transparent md:hidden"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="md:w-1/2 p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Wealth Switch</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">Unlock your financial potential with our revolutionary wealth-building algorithm. Take control of your financial destiny!</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <a 
                    href="https://www.digistore24.com/redir/413844/CrimsonEdge/" 
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full bg-primary-600 text-white py-3 px-6 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-primary-700 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200"
                  >
                    Activate Wealth Switch
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-600">Still have questions? <a href="/contact" class="text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium">Contact us</a> and we'll be happy to help!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .space-y-8 > :not([hidden]) ~ :not([hidden]) {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .space-y-6 > :not([hidden]) ~ :not([hidden]) {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }
  .space-y-4 > :not([hidden]) ~ :not([hidden]) {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
